      • ALPS_MAX_AGE_LAST_LAYER

        public static final int ALPS_MAX_AGE_LAST_LAYER
        there is no age-limit to the last layer so as to be able to keep the best individuals from the most promising (longest running) search. Thus with 6 age layers, a polynomial aging-scheme and an age gap of 20 the maximum ages for the layers are: 20, 40, 80, 180, 320 and infinity.
